quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,"Che, Ruri; ka ngoeli"
  74,33,Le ka bosiu ha bo esa
  74,34,Le ka meso ha mafube a hlaha
  74,35,Sena empa e le se seng sa lits’upiso tse kholohali
  74,36,Temoso ho batho
  74,37,Ho e mong le e mong oa lona ea khethang tsela e nepahetseng
  74,38,Phefomoloho ka ngoe e tla paka liketso tsa eona
  74,39,Kantle le balekane ba letsoho la molema
  74,40,"Lirapeng: ba tla botsana"
  74,41,Ba botse baetsalibe
  74,42,“Ke eng se le isitseng Mollong-oa-Lihele?”
  74,43,"Ba tla re: “Re bile sieo ho ba neng ba rapela”"
  74,44,“Kapa ba neng ba fepa mafutsana
  74,45,“Re ne re le mokhatlong oa basomi
  74,46,“Re ne re latola Letsatsi la Kahlolo
  74,47,“Ho fihlela lefu le re oela holimo.”
  74,48,Ha ho na ‘muelli ea tla bang molemo ho bona
  74,49,Joale molato ke eng ka bona hobane ba ile ba furalla temoso
  74,50,Joaloka ha eka ke lipokola li ts’ohile
  74,51,Li baleha tau
  74,52,"Mehlolo, mong le mong o batla ho fuoa maqhepe a manolotsoeng"
  74,53,"Che, ha ba na letsoalo la Bo-tlang"
  74,54,"Che, Ruri sena ke temoso"
  74,55,Mong le mong ea nang le hona a inkele temoso
  74,56,"Empa ha ho mong ea tla e boloka ka khopolo, kantle ho thato ea Allah: ke Mong`a Botlehali, le tsoarelo"